letters={"Q","W","E","R","T","Z","U","I","O","P","A","S","D","F","G","H","J","K","L","Y","X","C","V","B","N","M"," "} s=screen readID=1 nameMem="...NAME LOADING..." name="...NAME LOADING..." mem={} function aScrTxt(ypos,text,speed,screenW) lc=string.len(text) if sC==nil or sC<-(10+(lc*5)) then if (lc*5)<screenW then sC=(lc*5) else sC=screenW end end if sC>0 then screen.drawText(1,ypos,text) else screen.drawText(sC,ypos,text) end sC=sC-speed end function onTick() secc=0 for i,pr in ipairs(mem) do if pr==0 then secc=secc+1 end end if secc>100 then mem={} end pos={} for i=1,5,1 do if input.getNumber(i*3-1)==readID then table.insert(pos,10*(i-1)+2) end end if input.getNumber(6*3-1)==readID then terminal=true else terminal=false end r=input.getNumber(readID*3) if r==pr then table.insert(mem,r) end count=0 ps=0 for i,cr in ipairs(mem) do if cr==269 and ps~=269 then count=count+1 end ps=cr end if count>1 then sta=1 cr=mem[sta] ps=0 while cr==269 or ps~=269 do sta=sta+1 cr=mem[sta] ps=mem[sta-1] end while cr~=269 do sta=sta+1 cr=mem[sta] ps=mem[sta-1] if cr==268 and ps~=268 then name=name..letters[ps] end end mem={} nameMem=name name="" end pr=r end
function onDraw() s.setColor(150,150,150) s.drawRectF(0,0,64,64) s.setColor(0,0,40) s.drawRectF(0,50,64,64-50) s.setColor(0,0,0) for i,p in ipairs(pos) do aScrTxt(42-p,nameMem,0.1,64) end s.setColor(150,150,150) if terminal then aScrTxt(54,nameMem,0.1,64) end end
